### Variables
@headChefId = 1
@lineCookId = 3

### GET by ID
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions/1
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

### GET all - no filters
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

### GET all - status PENDING
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?status=PENDING
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

### GET all - status APPROVED
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?status=APPROVED

### GET all - status REJECTED
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?status=REJECTED

### GET all - invalid status → 400
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?status=INVALID

### GET all - week + year
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?week=12&year=2026

### GET all - week + year + status PENDING
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?week=12&year=2026&status=PENDING

### GET all - week + year + status APPROVED
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?week=12&year=2026&status=APPROVED

### GET all - week without year → 400 (must come together)
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?week=10

### GET all - year without week → 400 (must come together)
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?year=2026

### GET all - week out of range → 400
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?week=99&year=2026

### GET all - year out of range → 400
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?week=10&year=1800

### GET all - stationId filter
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?stationId=1

### GET all - stationId + status PENDING
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?stationId=2&status=PENDING

### GET all - full filter: status + week + year + stationId + orderBy
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?status=PENDING&week=13&year=2026&stationId=1&orderBy=status

### GET all - orderBy station
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?orderBy=station

### GET all - orderBy unknown value → falls back to default order (no error)
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions?orderBy=invalid_column

### GET current week - all statuses
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions/current-week

### GET current week - PENDING only
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions/current-week?status=PENDING

### GET current week - APPROVED only
GET {{url}}/dish-suggestions/current-week?status=APPROVED

### POST create suggestion (Salmon)
POST {{url}}/dish-suggestions/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenLineCook}}}

{
    "nameDA": "Laks med beurre blanc",
    "descriptionDA": "Færøsk laks bagt med fransk smør sauce",
    "stationId": 1,
    "allergenIds": [1, 4],
    "targetWeek": 16,
    "targetYear": 2026
}

### POST create suggestion (Butter chicken)
POST {{url}}/dish-suggestions
Content-Type: application/json
X-Dev-User-Id: {{lineCookId}}

{
    "nameDA": "Butter Chicken",
    "descriptionDA": "Marineret kylling i cremet og aromatisk curry-sauce med stegte blomkål og ris",
    "stationId": 1,
    "allergenIds": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
    "targetWeek": 14,
    "targetYear": 2026
}

### PUT update suggestion
PUT {{url}}/dish-suggestions/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Dev-User-Id: {{lineCookId}}

{
    "nameDA": "Laks med citron og kapers",
    "descriptionDA": "Frisk laks med citron, dild og kapers",
    "allergenIds": [1, 2, 4]
}

### PUT update suggestion allergens
PUT {{url}}/dish-suggestions/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Dev-User-Id: {{lineCookId}}

{
    "nameDA": "Laks med citron og kapers",
    "descriptionDA": "Frisk laks med citron, dild og kapers",
    "allergenIds": []
}

### PATCH approve suggestion
PATCH {{url}}/dish-suggestions/7/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}


### PATCH reject suggestion
PATCH {{url}}/dish-suggestions/5/reject
Content-Type: application/json
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

{
    "feedback": "Retten passer ikke til menuen - for tung til forår"
}


### PATCH reject - blank feedback
PATCH {{url}}/dish-suggestions/2/reject
Content-Type: application/json
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

{
    "feedback": ""
}

### DELETE - Delete suggestions
DELETE {{local}}/dish-suggestions/3
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}
